# NAME: Speedtest
# AUTHOR: Codex
# UPDATED: 2026-06-14
# FORMAT: Surge Ruleset
# SOURCES: SukkaW/Surge, Ookla, Cloudflare, LibreSpeed, blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script, QuixoticHeart/rule-set
# NOTE: Public speed-test platforms and stable test backends.
# NOTE: Volatile per-ISP nodes are covered by specific hostname keywords where practical.

# Stable test backends hosted on shared infrastructure
DOMAIN,mensura.cdn-apple.com
DOMAIN,open.cachefly.net
DOMAIN,wifiman-stability-test.ubncloud.com
DOMAIN,wifiman.ubncloud.com

# Speed-test platforms and measurement networks
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,fast.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,librespeed.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,measurement-lab.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,measurementlab.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,nperf.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pingtest.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,speed.cloudflare.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,speed.googlefiber.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,speedcheck.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,speedof.me
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,speedsmart.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,testmy.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,wifiman.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,wifiman.me

# Dynamic test node hostnames using explicit service names
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,ookla
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,speedtest
